{"id": "1265504980312526898", "channel_id": "1265504980312526898", "type": 0, "author_id": "1231540652253253705", "author_name": "menoctus", "author_bot": false, "content": "大家好，這裡是難忘今宵攻略組，這次為大家帶來的是奧爾拉支線地圖。\n\n（地圖皮膚忘了改）\n\n注意：\n\n紅地板「血污之池」：經過後消失，可選失去全部狂氣並刪除1張症狀卡/ 回復血量並被塞2張症狀卡；或在點亮共鳴【銀鑰洗禮】後，使用所有銀鑰能量清除。\n\nuid: 100001547\n\n新版：", "timestamp": "2024-07-24T03:04:59.252000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [{"emoji": "🍟", "emoji_id": null, "count": 1}], "attachments": [{"id": "1265504982803939411", "filename": "LONG.jpg", "content_type": "image/jpeg", "size": 3992195, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1265504980312526898/1265504982803939411/LONG.jpg?ex=69cbe29b&is=69ca911b&hm=bc0ae3413670bb4fd6be6e61a4743d118966af3f1baf32519fce76b008f89526&"}], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1265504980312526898", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "特遣紀錄「玫瑰的棲居」關卡地圖總覽", "forum_channel_id": "1174179624096378930", "thread_tags": ["1260133992636743681", "1181143392739147778"]}
